{"tid":1363324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田區議會要人，街坊快落","createTime":"2019-07-25T06:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T07:07:34.000Z","uid":267730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"43ab7d49ff32b51891b3997ee94123c71ed6e3f1","tid":1363324,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:44:51.000Z","msg":"轉<br />\n<br />\n今天2:00後沙田區議會大會（會議2:30開始）<br />\n<br />\n會議地點：沙田政合署4樓，歡迎大家在觀眾席監察議員工作。<br />\n<br />\n大量藍絲同建制狗議員玩野，近既即刻落去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=872337159808525&amp;id=200954406608272\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D872337159808525%26id%3D200954406608272&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUf%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=2e59afa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=872337159808525&amp;id=200954406608272</a>"},{"pid":"4889da6b8fd2a16becb759d7b227b6ec806616bc","tid":1363324,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:45:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e337cc65693011a65cc6f5543d8a5a942f08bd7","tid":1363324,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:45:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82e6fca22177262578552d30c31722992b09bcc8","tid":1363324,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:48:41.000Z","msg":"要人"},{"pid":"3b51e69b9bd8fc836ecf87cd9a7b62dedbbbb99b","tid":1363324,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:48:51.000Z","msg":"要人"},{"pid":"c4993e9e01612ceaad3a0e5bed999ad6d23b9756","tid":1363324,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:49:01.000Z","msg":"要人"},{"pid":"25d40ab10c8afed028258aa962f80f121aa351d2","tid":1363324,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:51:42.000Z","msg":"要人"},{"pid":"e02a420e2f9ebf52fbe33d4da08ae4f7d1287c57","tid":1363324,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:51:53.000Z","msg":"sos"},{"pid":"44f51e3a5ae1de909897b5f7918b94854118d841","tid":1363324,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:53:58.000Z","msg":"【即時】(14:51) 沙田區議會原定下午兩點半舉行會議，但民政處以公眾席滿座為由，拒絕記者進場。<br />\n<br />\n臨近會議開始時間，民主派沙田區議員程張迎、陳兆陽及麥潤培，與記者及市民一同進入會議室。<br />\n<br />\n沙田區議會主席何厚祥進入會議室，稱會場情況混亂，宣布休會15分鐘。建制派議員亦離席，現時市民留在會議室，將memo紙貼在牆上。<br />\n<br />\n直播：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Y1w1yI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Y1w1yI&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUf%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=e364e289\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Y1w1yI</a>"},{"pid":"1945ca2fdac331000c88f29ba2b12aa8e0aca36c","tid":1363324,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:55:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45c47b010adae00d46a435133c3e2089ba6ff1ea","tid":1363324,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:58:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3585fd6a618cf76768eba7e6ce980220274d5b49","tid":1363324,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:03:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97c783d622fb9885e5773e99f85f0b50fe276511","tid":1363324,"uid":2210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:04:16.000Z","msg":"沙田冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f727e6ef4abdd6e695d814d9677283020b86ae","tid":1363324,"uid":2210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:04:49.000Z","msg":"live<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/inmediahk/videos/872337159808525/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Finmediahk%2Fvideos%2F872337159808525%2F&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUf%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=d090d9d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/inmediahk/videos/8723371598085